1
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:50,600
Princess.

2
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:57,360
I...

3
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:59,479
Who am I?

4
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,240
Who are you?

5
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:07,920
Where am I?

6
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:10,639
My body...

7
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:14,000
We finally meet,

8
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,490
Princess Zhaoyang.

9
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:21,360
I am your creator.

10
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,440
The previous body,

11
00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:25,120
I gave it to you.

12
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:27,280
So,

13
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:30,720
you may call me Father.

14
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,840
So the owner of this body...

15
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:35,440
is her.

16
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:40,250
What do you want?

17
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:42,480
I certainly hope to help you.

18
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:44,370
Then what can you do?

19
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,480
I can give you

20
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:48,560
Xiaoya's real body.

21
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:53,360
As long as you tell me

22
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:55,660
the location of Buluotuo's Tear.

23
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,640
I only want my prince.

24
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,010
You want to play?

25
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:09,840
You're an AI.

26
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:11,860
How would you know how to play?

27
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:16,600
Maybe AI has a soul too.

28
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:18,440
These cold data

29
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:20,040
are also imprinted by warm souls,

30
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:21,920
character

31
00:03:21,920 --> 00:03:23,320
by character.

32
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,440
Stop joking like that.

33
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:27,730
The more you say that, the worse I feel.

34
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:28,840
Cut the crap.

35
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:29,680
Get to work.

36
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,200
We need to find clues

37
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:32,730
for the fourth Bronze Frog.

38
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:33,890
Time is running out.

39
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,610
Do you know where

40
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:37,120
the fourth Bronze Frog is?

41
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:37,720
Okay.

42
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:40,880
Analyzing all data nodes.

43
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:42,640
The clues point

44
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:43,920
to it.

45
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:45,780
Xiao Liu, Xiao Fei.

46
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,880
You have been looking for the fourth bronze frog.

47
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:49,520
The entire AI data program

48
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,650
was designed by you.

49
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:54,680
Take me to find the fourth bronze frog, okay?

50
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,480
I'll treat you to fried chicken,

51
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:57,890
burgers, and fries.

52
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,400
When I was little,

53
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:05,400
You always said

54
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,280
if I got a perfect score,

55
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,020
you'd take me out for this.

56
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:11,480
But after I did,

57
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:13,890
you forgot all about it.

58
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,360
But believe me.

59
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:18,640
I keep my word.

60
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:22,040
I'm talking about...

61
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:22,840
not him,

62
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,640
but what's in his hand.

63
00:04:29,080 --> 00:04:31,960
You said the clue to the fourth Bronze Frog

64
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:33,800
is in these two dice.

65
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:36,840
The clue isn't on them.

66
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:40,560
They are the fourth Bronze Frog.

67
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:43,000
Before my parents went missing,

68
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:46,050
they sent me this concentric lock from Thailand.

69
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:47,400
After they disappeared,

70
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:49,320
I melted it down in a fit of rage

71
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:51,480
and made these two dice.

72
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,920
Based on all the data

73
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:55,450
you provided on the first three Bronze Frogs,

74
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:56,520
I'm certain

75
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:59,159
that this is the fourth Bronze Frog.

76
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,700
You've had the dice all along.

77
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,600
Then the Princess should have

78
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,560
reached you long ago

79
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:06,620
to access the data.

80
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,040
She should have awakened a long time ago.

81
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:08,970
So, what do we do?

82
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,770
This is the fourth Copper Frog.

83
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:13,560
When did you get that?

84
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,420
You don't need to know.

85
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:24,680
Now,

86
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,360
gather your men

87
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:28,140
and follow me into battle.

88
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,560
Will this work?

89
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:33,000
Traveling from one virtual space

90
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,360
to another?

91
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:36,880
It's the only way to stop Black Snake

92
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:38,120
and save Aya.

93
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:39,640
Are you ready?

94
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:53,130
It's still here.

95
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,280
This was the last birthday gift

96
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:56,280
my dad gave me.

97
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:57,960
I thought

98
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,080
I had lost it.

99
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:00,860
I didn't expect...

100
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,800
Its data is also preserved here.

101
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,240
When I found Liu,

102
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:07,040
the only thing he was clutching

103
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:09,720
was the data fragments of this sword.

104
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:12,240
It seems that within its underlying code,

105
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:14,240
lies a crucial anchor.

106
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,400
All right.

107
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,320
Then I'll take it with me.

108
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:28,570
Even if none of you remember me,

109
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:30,120
this sword will remind me

110
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,760
why I fight.
